01:20:48.159 --> 01:20:49.628
My son is free.

01:20:54.931 --> 01:20:56.967
This ain't no matinee, darlin'!

01:21:00.904 --> 01:21:04.872
You! Jien of deceit.

01:21:04.874 --> 01:21:06.974
Go to hell!

